metadata.name: 800 db - Pixel Perfect
metadata.description: Dalton Mannerud is changing the game with his debut project 'Out of Bounds' under his new alias '800 db'. 'Pixel Perfect' is an audio-visual experience that pushes the boundaries of modern art. This collection features 14 mesmerizing 3D visuals perfectly paired with ambient, electronic, synth-heavy tracks infused with a touch of hip-hop. The project takes you on a journey through a world of soundscapes, immersing you in an experience like no other.
